@example
                                          (3 4)
                                            |
                                            V
((1 2) 3 4)  +---+---+                  +---+---+     +---+---+
        ---->| * | *-+----------------->| * | *-+---->| * | / |
             +-|-+---+                  +-|-+---+     +-|-+---+
               |                          |             |
               V                          V             V
      (1 2)  +---+---+     +---+---+    +---+         +---+
        ---->| * | *-+---->| * | / |    | 3 |         | 4 |
             +-|-+---+     +-|-+---+    +---+         +---+
               |             |
               V             V
             +---+         +---+
